title: 1974–75 Northern Football League
text:
The 1974–75 Northern Football League season was the 77th in the history of <a href="Northern%20Football%20League">Northern Football League</a>, a <a href="association%20football">football</a> competition in England.
Clubs.
Division One featured 19 clubs which competed in the league last season, no new clubs joined the division this season.
